snippet.title: CAPTAIN SODA: Pop pop pop!
snippet.description:
SHOOT SODA, BECOME THE COLA MAN! 

Play as Captain Soda and use soft drinks to defend Earth against an alien apocalypse. 
'Super Crate Box' meets 'Hell is Other Demons' in this satisfying arcade platform shooter about refreshing chemical warfare. 

Wishlist it on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1862950/Captain_Soda/
